"" Window management mapping
" opening closing windows
map <Leader>w- <C-w>s
map <Leader>w/ <C-w>v
map <Leader>wc <C-w>q
map <Leader>wo <C-w>m
map <Leader>wT <C-w>t
" move between windows
map <Leader>ww <C-w>w
map <Leader>wh <C-w><left>
map <Leader>wj <C-w><down>
map <Leader>wk <C-w><up>
map <Leader>wl <C-w><right>
map <Leader>wn <C-w>n
" move windows
map <Leader>wH <C-w>H
map <Leader>wJ <C-w>J
map <Leader>wK <C-w>K
map <Leader>wL <C-w>L
